org.gvsig.tools.service

Class AbstractPersistentService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.tools.service.AbstractService
      • org.gvsig.tools.service.AbstractPersistentService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Persistent, Service

    public abstract class AbstractPersistentService
extends AbstractService
implements Persistent
    Base Service implementation which is also Persistent.

    The persistence is based on the service parameters, which are persisted by this implementation. Child implementation services must persist their own additional properties.
